# .trivyignore — project-scoped CVE allowlist.
# Format: <CVE-ID>     # owner=<gh-handle> sunset:YYYY-MM-DD reason
# CI fails when any sunset date is past and the entry still exists.

# Example entry — remove before first use.
# CVE-2025-12345        # owner=@ruslan sunset:2026-09-01 transient false-positive in test fixture
